{"tid":1900130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"糗！中國外交部新任發言人 被抓包推特追蹤AV女優","createTime":"2020-02-27T04:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T05:48:14.000Z","uid":89543,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d871eba2c6a165ef0248f5410dd9126098e83b49","tid":1900130,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoaBhGS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoaBhGS.png&h=3fceded7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時新聞／綜合報導〕中國外交部近日插曲不斷，先是發言人華春瑩被人發現按讚要求習近平的貼文；又傳出新任的發言人趙立堅追蹤了前AV女優蒼井空的帳號。消息傳出後，在推特引發網友熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅推特帳號擁有25萬粉絲，上任外交部發言人後被稱為「網紅發言人」，不過就在趙立堅上任第二天，有網友發現他的推特帳號竟追蹤了前AV女優蒼井空的帳號；另有網友實測表示，他同時追蹤了趙立堅與蒼井空後，再點開蒼井空的推特帳號，的確能看到趙立堅追蹤了蒼井空。雖目前趙立堅已經取消追蹤蒼井空，但截圖已經在推特上被廣傳。"},{"pid":"c8db752dd1dc533303b1113736982cb4d718ad86","tid":1900130,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:57:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3081132?fbclid=IwAR0LWQrTmm-bxn9P0kfZmulBOc56sursftrTZXpXk0SOeFy_q4nUyeTBu2I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3081132%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0LWQrTmm-bxn9P0kfZmulBOc56sursftrTZXpXk0SOeFy_q4nUyeTBu2I&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=ee6f898e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3081132%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0LWQrTmm-bxn9P0kfZmulBOc56sursftrTZXpXk0SOeFy_q4nUyeTBu2I&h=f9cff9d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3081132?fbclid=IwAR0LWQrTmm-bxn9P0kfZmulBOc56sursftrTZXpXk0SOeFy_q4nUyeTBu2I</a>"},{"pid":"c7522f2e5b7240d62b7fffa6353edebe1a18c18d","tid":1900130,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T04:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c93fde02b9df0e3bc5d20090a1f8e8